<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">What? No, he did not say that. The little girl was not killed BY a woman talking on the phone. She wandered into the street and was hit by a car while<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">What? No, he did not say that. The little girl was not killed BY a woman talking on the phone. She wandered into the street and was hit by a car while the woman (her mother) who was supposed to be watching her was in the house talking on the phone.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
